      <title>习近平在最新发表的讲话中敦促党赢得台湾的支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-16/xi-urged-party-to-win-taiwan-support-in-newly-released-speech</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国家主席习近平在台湾选出亲美总统后于本周发表的一篇旧讲话中敦促执政的共产党更好地赢得台湾人民的心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-16/xi-urged-party-to-win-taiwan-support-in-newly-released-speech</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 02:05:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚与洛克希德·马丁公司签署导弹制造协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-16/australia-signs-missile-manufacturing-pact-with-lockheed-martin</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚公布了最早于明年根据与美国军火巨头洛克希德马丁公司签订的价值 3700 万澳元（2450 万美元）的合同生产第一批国产导弹的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-16/australia-signs-missile-manufacturing-pact-with-lockheed-martin</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 01:56:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投票开始后不久，特朗普前往爱荷华州党团会议获胜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-16/trump-cruises-to-iowa-caucus-victory</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前总统唐纳德·特朗普在爱荷华州党团会议中轻松获胜，抵挡住了竞争对手罗恩·德桑蒂斯和妮基·黑利的挑战，巩固了他在竞选中作为共和党明显领跑者的地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-16/trump-cruises-to-iowa-caucus-victory</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 01:35:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗对伊拉克和叙利亚境内的目标进行致命轰炸</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-16/iran-strikes-targets-in-iraq-over-soleimani-memorial-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗伊斯兰革命卫队向伊拉克北部和叙利亚的目标发射了导弹，据称是对本月卡西姆·苏莱马尼将军墓地附近发生的恐怖袭击造成近 100 人死亡的报复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-16/iran-strikes-targets-in-iraq-over-soleimani-memorial-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 01:11:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜终止统一机构以向首尔施压</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-16/north-korea-ends-agencies-for-reunification-to-pressure-seoul</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜领导人金正恩称韩国是对平壤最具敌意的国家，因为朝鲜政府废除了致力于统一的机构，为高度军事化的半岛带来新的紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-16/north-korea-ends-agencies-for-reunification-to-pressure-seoul</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 01:07:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登挑战者菲利普斯提名马斯克和阿克曼担任内阁职务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/biden-challenger-phillips-floats-musk-ackman-for-cabinet-roles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[众议员迪恩·菲利普斯 (Dean Phillips) 提出，如果他在民主党总统竞选中入主白宫，潘兴广场资本管理公司 (Pershing Square Capital Management) 的比尔·阿克曼 (Bill Ackman)、X 所有者埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 和天使投资人杰森·卡拉卡尼斯 (Jason Calacanis) 可能会加入内阁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/biden-challenger-phillips-floats-musk-ackman-for-cabinet-roles</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 23:35:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新西兰绿党议员因入店行窃指控辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/nz-green-party-lawmaker-resigns-after-shoplifting-allegations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰绿党议员戈尔里兹·加赫拉曼 (Golriz Ghahraman) 在商店行窃指控后以心理健康问题为由辞职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/nz-green-party-lawmaker-resigns-after-shoplifting-allegations</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 23:18:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普领先爱荷华州预选，共和党争夺亚军</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/republicans-battle-for-runner-up-as-trump-leads-iowa-caucuses</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据熟悉竞选活动的人士透露，随着亚军争夺战进入白热化阶段，唐纳德·特朗普在共和党总统候选人提名中最接近的三位竞争对手都认为，在爱荷华州党团会议中获得第二名的机会很大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/republicans-battle-for-runner-up-as-trump-leads-iowa-caucuses</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 23:12:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>爱荷华州最新消息：策略师称，晚期县可能有利于海利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/iowa-caucus-2024-latest-on-trump-haley-and-desantis-on-campaign-trail</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据多家新闻媒体报道，前总统唐纳德·特朗普在爱荷华州党团会议中轻松获胜，巩固了他作为共和党 2024 年提名的明显领跑者的地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/iowa-caucus-2024-latest-on-trump-haley-and-desantis-on-campaign-trail</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 15:24:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
